Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法鲁多被CIA逮捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「{\1c&H0000FF&}蛇{\r}」先前在CIA内部有眼线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但已经被处理掉了 就算我们不行动…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工厂运送「花苞」的车被「{\1c&H0000FF&}蛇{\r}」袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若有幸存者 则进行营救
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,袭击者可能就是「花苞」本身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们容易被捕就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是日本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明知故问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道翻花绳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通过活动指尖使大脑活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对预防痴呆有一定效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我的表情很吓人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:30.84,Default,,0000,0096,0000,,{\fs36}UA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs32}「UA」是斯瓦希里语「花」的意思 同时意味着「死」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你就是在我心头盛开的花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热闹的庙会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 让我检查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这又不是数码的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片要经过精心冲洗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能成为大泽玛丽亚的眼睛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很有志气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这样的摄影师是混不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.66,0:09:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报道之神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只把机会留给有准备的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 实先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真亏您能得到在这里设立外资PMC的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs34}（PMC：Private Millitary Contractor 私营军事承包商）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我事先做足了工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点投资 打一仗就收回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个国家就简单在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请务必把资产运作交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 开发部门好像也有些有趣的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您知道所谓「联觉」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,视觉 听觉 味觉 触觉 嗅觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相互独立的五感同时作用之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被称为「联觉者」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文字会带上颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声音会化为可见的实体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,具体形式因人而异
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想更进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考虑能否把它用在敌我识别上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动用五感认知通过视觉得到的情报…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在动身去迎接姐姐之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要先沐浴净身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有联觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也能通过净化后的肌肤感知到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.27,0:10:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,低沉的心跳让我的腹肌震颤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强烈的心跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我体内的「{\1c&H0000FF&\3c&HFF0055&\blur2}红{\r}」熊熊燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的秘书在洗澡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梁琪 拿华尔街报告来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.39,0:11:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 没事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊… 多谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社长 差不多到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实先生到哪里去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目不转睛地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正视这个未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.33,0:12:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这就是她所见的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我听不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.48,0:13:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生命的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家一直 一直想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你却杳无音信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俯下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还在和坏人战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应当说 是些蠢货吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听不懂耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是我打中的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人 想找茬的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说迦南…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这个布娃娃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它没有颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在可是庙会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.46,0:16:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手背过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 这样就动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是根线罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一扯就断…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要扯断它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏有它 我们才成为朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你使坏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点痴呆的老人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和精心照顾他的孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.63,0:17:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 多么美好的场面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我找错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想来 这也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来 大泽…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好华丽的表演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:18:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这可不是闹着玩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙… 以为这是什么余兴节目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.25,0:18:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 现实就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们却故意视而不见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梁琪小姐 是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,软蛋 多用点力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唔 唔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？！ 迦南？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.17,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈柯 你也在这里等着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大泽 要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迦南她 还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的生命 如此绚烂夺目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至无法直视
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想去碰触
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很高兴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真死板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小丫头真是「{\1c&H0000FF&}蛇{\r}」的老大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯恐天下不乱的武装集团…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是媒体大肆渲染
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混淆了视听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&H0000FF&}蛇{\r}终究是{\1c&H000000\3c&HFFFFFF\bord2}蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只会在地上爬来爬去罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前卫被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是路边炸弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停车 马上给我停车！
